title: Organic Coffee Stare Miasto
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Bakery, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Certified organic cafe serving breakfast, soups, pies, cakes, cookies, coffee, tea and juices. Offers any drink with vegetable milk. The soup and some cakes and cookies are vegan. Some of the cakes are also gluten-free. The juices use superfood supplements. Has another location in the city center.
